# React Component Patterns

## UI Primitives
Use shared components from `frontend/src/components/ui/`:
- `Card` (sizes: sm, md, lg), `Button` (variants: primary, secondary, danger)
- `Badge`, `Tabs`/`TabPanel`, `Modal`
- `useToast()` hook for notifications: `toast.success()`, `toast.error()`

## Navigation
- RIA sidebar: `frontend/src/components/dashboard/Sidebar.tsx` — collapsible menu groups
- Client portal sidebar: `frontend/src/components/portal/PortalNav.tsx`
- Add new pages to groups in sidebar config, not as top-level items

## Styling
- Tailwind CSS only — no CSS modules or styled-components
- Blue/white/green brand palette: `blue-600`, `emerald-500`, `slate-*` for neutrals
- Sidebar background: `bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1e3a5f] to-[#0f2744]`

## Accessibility
- Add `aria-label` to all icon-only buttons (required for E2E test selectors)
- Use semantic HTML: `role="tab"` for tabs, `role="tabpanel"` for content
- Buttons that change text (e.g., "Copy" → "Copied!") need stable `aria-label`

## Error Handling
- Wrap async clipboard/API calls in try/catch for headless browser compatibility
- Use error boundaries for page-level crash protection
